      "name": "Personal Knowledge System",
      "abstract": "Personal knowledge systems connect digital gardens, wikis, note archives, research methods, backlinks and long-term intellectual memory.",
      "description": "A personal knowledge system is a practice and tool environment for capturing, linking, revising and retrieving notes, sources, ideas and decisions over time.",
